OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright, cold start
OL,6,Fcloud increasing through the morning.
OL,7,FCoastal showers pushing inland through
OL,8,Fthe day, easing off by the evening
OL,9,Fwith some brighter spells developing.
OL,10,FFeeling cool, particularly along
OL,11,Fcoasts in northeasterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSunny spells persist through
OL,14,Fthe evening. Temperatures fall quickly
OL,15,Fovernight, with a rural frost likely
OL,16,Fin the east, before cloud thickens
OL,17,Ffrom the west later helping
OL,18,Ftemperatures to recover here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
